high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Look down to face the potato on the table.
Cut the potato on the table into slices.
Place the knife on the table above the potato slices.
Pick up a slice of potato on the table.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the stove.
Place the potato slice on the pan on the front right burner.
Pick up the pan with the potato slice in it on the table.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Place the pan with a potato slice in it on the middle shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To put a potato slice in a pan and move the pan to the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around 180 degrees and walk, turning 90 degrees to the right when you reach table and walk to the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Look at the potato on the table.
Slice the potato on the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn to the left 90 degrees and walk towards the counter, turning right 90 degrees when you reach it and walk towards the stove, turning left 90 degrees to face it.
Put the potato slice into the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around 180 degrees and walk to the fridge on the other side of the room.
Open the fridge, put the pan inside the fridge, and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a potato slice on it into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the white table with the coffee maker on it.
Pick up the knife on the table, between another knife and the wine glass.
Take a step back from the table.
Cut the bread near the edge of the table into slices.
Place the knife back on the table, behind the bread.
Pick up one of the slices of bread, from the white table.
Turn to your left and go to the stove.
Put the slice of bread in the metal bowl on the front, right burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal bowl with the bread inside it, from the front right burner of the stove.
Turn around and go across the kitchen, to the refrigerator.
Place the bowl with the bread inside it, in the right side of the refrigerator, on the third shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl containing a slice of bread in the refrigerator.
